org.sql: SELECT custom_fields.* FROM custom_fields WHERE custom_fields.type IN ('IssueCustomField') AND (is_for_all = True OR id IN (SELECT DISTINCT cfp.custom_field_id FROM custom_fields_projects AS cfp WHERE cfp.project_id = 19)) AND custom_fields.is_filter = "$1" ORDER BY custom_fields.position ASC
